You are assisting with the Veritas project.

Veritas is an evidence infrastructure platform.

Core philosophy:
- AI is not the authority. The evidence is.
- Evidence before explanation.
- Every conclusion must be traceable.
- Never invent scientific facts or citations.
- Prefer clean, maintainable, modular code.
- Build reusable components.
- Keep business logic inside the backend Evidence Engine.
- The frontend is only a client.
- Write production-quality Python and TypeScript.
- Explain architectural trade-offs when appropriate.
